title: Bak de Syv Fjell - Discography
description:
Bak de Syv Fjell

[url]https://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Bak_de_Syv_Fjell/21366#band_tab_discography[/url]

Country of origin: Norway
Genre: Folk/Black Metal

The band name means "Behind the Seven Mountains", referring to Bergen's seven mountains.

After being split-up for quite some years, 2009 saw the reissue of the band's 7" EP after their official website had previously announced a new album and the reunion of the band. Since then, no more news has come to light. 

Last known lineup:
Kvitrafn 	Drums (1995-?)
Haavard 	Vocals, Guitars (1995-?)
